# ~VAGRANT~

## Install process

### Terminal commands

~ cd Desktop/dev-ops/intro

➜  intro vagrant up

➜  intro vagrant provision

➜  intro vagrant up

➜  intro vagrant init ubuntu/xenial64

➜  intro ls

➜  intro vagrant ssh

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ sudo apt-get update -y

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ sudo apt-get install nginx -y

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ curl localhost:80

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ exit

➜  intro vagrant reload

➜  intro cat /etc/hosts

➜  intro vagrant plugin install vagrant-hostsupdater

➜  intro cat /etc/hosts

➜  intro vagrant destroy

*copy any environments/apps or folders into working directory*

➜  intro vagrant up

➜  intro vagrant ssh

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ sudo apt-get update -y

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ sudo apt-get install nginx -y

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ exit

➜  intro git init

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ git add .

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ git commit -m "first commit"

➜  intro git:(master) git remote add origin git@github.com:DragosTirlungeanu/Vagrant-intro.git

➜  intro git:(master) git push -u origin master

➜  intro git:(master) vagrant reload

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ vagrant ssh

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:~$ cd /home/ubuntu/app/

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:/home/ubuntu/app$ ls

vagrant@ubuntu-xenial:/home/ubuntu/app$ exit

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ cd environment/spec-tests

➜  spec-tests git:(master) ✗ bundle

➜  spec-tests git:(master) ✗ rake spec

➜  app git:(master) ✗ touch provision.sh

➜  app git:(master) ✗ cd ...

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ vagrant destroy

➜  intro git:(master) ✗ cd app

➜  app git:(master) ✗ ls

README.md    node_modules seeds
app.js       package.json test
models       provision.sh views
modules      public